title: Angels score 5 in 9th, beat Rangers 11-10
text:
> Texas Angels score 5 in 9th, beat Rangers 11-10 Texas Rangers' Elvis Andrus dives safely in to third base advancing from second on a fly ball out by teammate Rougned Odor during the second inning of a baseball game against the Los Angeles Angels in Arlington, Texas, Saturday, Oct. 3, 2015.
